# Functions for handling Emacs windows on a 24" (1920x1200) monitor.

AddToFunc MyMaximizeEmacsLeft
+ I Focus
+ I Raise
+ I Move 0p 0p
+ I Resize 954p 1167p
+ I WarpToWindow 50 7p

AddToFunc MyMaximizeEmacsRight
+ I Focus
+ I Raise
+ I Move 960p 0p
+ I Resize 954p 1167p
+ I WarpToWindow 50 7p

# For reasons that remain obscure, the window geometry that FVWM picks up for
# Chrome is not the true geometry.

AddToFunc MyNormalizeChrome
+ I Focus
+ I Raise
+ I Move 0p 0p
+ I Resize 950p 1198p
+ I WarpToWindow 50 100p

AddToFunc MyMaximizeChrome
+ I Focus
+ I Raise
+ I Move 0p 0p
+ I Resize 1920p 1198p
+ I WarpToWindow 50 100p
